  │            USE FOR: NY ST-810, MA ST-9, PA EDI schedule      │
  │                                                              │
  │  TEXT    → Fallback: cluster chars by x-position            │
  │            USE FOR: MD-202 page 1 (sparse positioned text)  │
  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

DITTO PRINT RULES:
  ✓ Row labels (left column) preserved exactly from AI / text
  ✓ Numbers preserved as TEXT — never reformatted by Excel
  ✓ Multi-column forms: each column in correct Excel column
  ✓ Section headers → dark blue merged row
  ✓ Sub-headers → light blue row
  ✓ Values right-aligned, labels left-aligned
  ✓ Zero-data-loss sub-row overflow for collisions
  ✓ Blank separator lines preserved
  ✓ All pages → separate worksheets

INSTALL:
